gcc -Wall save-temps mian.c  


1) preprocessing
    all the comments get removed from the program and the data of library files get fetched i.e., stdio.h or math.h
    main.i contains the content at this stage

2) compiling
    code translate to assembly language
    main.s

3) assembling
    code translate to mashine language
    mian.o

4) linking
    connect all the .o files (mashine code files) with each other
    a) static linking
    b) dynamic linking